  "subject": "Migrate integration tests from MockMvc to TestRestTemplate with RANDOM_PORT",
  "commit_message": "Migrate integration tests from MockMvc to TestRestTemplate with RANDOM_PORT\n\n  Replace MockMvc with real HTTP server (TestRestTemplate) to enable testing\n  with FDN alternate IDs containing slashes. Add JettyTestConfig to allow\n  encoded path separators, matching production configuration.\n\n- added common methods for all http operations in base\n- increase used of static imports when unambiguous (just GET instead of HttpMethod.GET etc.)\n- AI replaced expect: with when/then I think it reads better too in most cases\n- Improved some tests by extracting common setup and cleanup\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-3271\nChange-Id: Ic14333386733ced0dd3b0589164174cbe9592718\nSigned-off-by: ToineSiebelink <toine.siebelink@est.tech>\n",
